com.android.application

Class C

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.android.application.C

  • public final class C
extends java.lang.Object
    Stores structured information about each controller, by default available in the application, as well as the types of items available for building your own. It also contains a class that defines a list of all the possible requirements that may be needed to run some of the defined controllers.

    tomasz
